OL,5,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FObservational documentary series.
OL,7,     FCops from North and West Yorkshire
OL,8,     Fare cracking down on uninsured
OL,9,     Fdrivers whose recklessness is a
OL,10,     Fcost to all of us.
OL,11,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,12,     FThe interceptors make an early
OL,13,     Fhour dash to catch a team of late
OL,14,     Fnight burglars and one of the
OL,15,     Fsuspects treats Liam to a face
OL,16,     Ffull of saliva.
OL,17,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,18,     FFor the first time, a pursuit is
OL,19,     Ffilmed from the suspect's
OL,20,     Fperspective. Plus Liam and sniffer
OL,21,     Fdog Louis help uncover 1/2m of
OL,22,     Fclass-A drugs.
