OL,5,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FWest Yorkshire is one of the UK's
OL,7,     Fhighest crime areas. With this
OL,8,     Fregion seeing criminal activity
OL,9,     Flevels rising, the Interceptors
OL,10,     Fuse every tool in their arsenal.
OL,11,G1700 Call the Bailiffs: Time to Pay Up!
OL,12,     FMark and Sam pursue over #180k
OL,13,     Ffrom a dentist, while Lewis chases
OL,14,     Fpayment for a classic car sold at
OL,15,     Fauction after the buyer tries to
OL,16,     Fback out due to unexpected repair
OL,17,     Fcosts.
OL,18,G1800 Home and Away
OL,19,     FTane lays down the law. Mackenzie
OL,20,     Fis hurting. Alf and John team up.
OL,21,     FSonny is intrigued by a stranger.
