OL,5,G2100 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,6,     FIn Orpington, a rescue team
OL,7,     Fbattles to save the life of an
OL,8,     Felderly motorist trapped in the
OL,9,     Fwreckage of his car. In Maidstone,
OL,10,     FParamedic Nathan provides urgent
OL,11,     Fcare at a hit and run.
OL,12,G2200 999: Critical Condition
OL,13,     FDocumentary series following the
OL,14,     Ftrauma and emergency teams at work
OL,15,     Fin a UK hospital. Patients include
OL,16,     Fa road accident victim and a man
OL,17,     Fwith a torn aorta.
