OL,5,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FIn this sporty episode, a boxing
OL,7,     Fcoach has a lipoma that looks like
OL,8,     Fan out-of-place ab, and a gym
OL,9,     Ffanatic has lumps on his arms that
OL,10,     Ffriends have mistaken for
OL,11,     Fodd-shaped muscles.
OL,12,G0000 Scam City: Don't Get Caught Out!
OL,13,     FIn Istanbul, a friendly
OL,14,     Fconversation at night may lead to
OL,15,     Fa bar bill of hundreds or even
OL,16,     Fthousands. If you can't pay,
OL,17,     Fyou're threatened with violence.
